Purpose: 
Develop a tool for todo table generation/modification/analisys

Arch description:
1. Todo table has txt format, is read, edited and highlighted(appropriate syntax highlight should be created) inside SublimeText(ST).
2. All actions with table are performed by hands in ST or using Py methods (assigned to hot keys or located in right-button-menu) processing todo.txt.
4. Table content is stored in db file (json or any other format) and should be loaded to txt file.
5. Todo table view/format is defined by set of configuration settings (default or defined by user)
6. A set of methods should be implemented(seems as ST plugin): generate todo tmpl...
